{{Databox|fr=Carl Friedrich Gauss}}'''Yuhan Kaṛl fridiritc guss''' (1777 - 1855) yan [[Tusnakt|usnak]] d [[Tasngama|usengam]] aliman, lli iskern tadaka d tyafut ɣ idɣaren ad n tussna (tasinakt d Tasengama). Ar as aqqran s "Agellid n usnaken" d "usnak lli kullu meqqurn zɣ assfal n ddunit". Guss ifka tugt i tasinakt d tussna, d iga ɣ inmɣuren n usnaken ɣ umezruy.

Ilul '''Guss''' ass n 30 bril 1777, izzri tamziyt nnes ɣ [[Brunswick]] ɣ [[Lalman|uliman]], d nettat aɣ iɣra. 

Mas ur teɣri d ur tessen tizi n tlalit n iwis kaṛl, mac rad stt id iledi netta d zɣiakud ann d aniɣ admzalalyn tmkfit nnes ɣ tasinakt.

Ɣ sskʷil rad yaf afessay i mennaw imukrisn ɣ tasinakt, mad lli rad issusem ''Duke n Brunswick'' lli rad t yazen s tzdawit n ''Collegium Carollinum'', ukan ar gis yaqqra ger 1792 d 1795, ar kiɣ immatti s tzdawit n ''Gottingen'', ukan ar daɣ yaqqra ger 1795 d 1798.

Ɣ isggʷasn dars iggʷran ɣ tzdawit, rad ifk '''Guss''' tugt n tdusi ɣ udɣar ad lli mu ikcem. Tugt n [[tmagunin]] rad tent isemd, d tiyaḍ rad ffɣen-t s ubaraz, d ugidi n imukrisn lli mu yad ttanfn isinaken zɣ zikk rad asn yaf afssay.

Ittussan '''Guss''' mas iga argaz n tuwuru, d iɣama f uncekk ann ar ass lliɣ immut ɣ 23 brayer 1855.

